article.headline: Brodeur scores 19 points, lifts Penn past Yale 69-61
article.linkText: Brodeur scores 19 points, lifts Penn past Yale 69-61
article.story: PHILADELPHIA -- AJ Brodeur posted 19 points, eight rebounds and five assists as Penn topped Yale 69-61 on Saturday night. Max Martz had 12 points for Penn (13-8, 5-3 Ivy League). Devon Goodman added 10 points. Paul Atkinson had 20 points and 10 rebounds for the Bulldogs (18-6, 6-2). Azar Swain added 13 points. Jordan Bruner had seven rebounds. Penn faces Dartmouth on the road on Friday. Yale matches up against Cornell on the road on Friday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
